terms_path = 'test_data/linear_terms.mat'
term = Selector(terms_path)
normalized_signals, Kalman_H, _, _ = term.make_selection()
kf = Kalman4FROLS(normalized_signals, Kalman_H=Kalman_H, uc=0.01)
y_coef = kf.estimate_coef()
